text: Listed may refer to: * Listed, Bornholm, a fishing village on the Danish island of Bornholm. * Listed (MMM program), a television show on MuchMoreMusic * Endangered species in biology * Listed building, in architecture, designation of a historically significant structure * Listed company, see listing (finance), a public company whose shares are traded e.g. on a stock exchange * UL Listed, a certification mark ==See also== * Listing (disambiguation)
